{"id": "art-59", "label": "Art. 59", "title": "Art. 59", "slug": "art-59", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 59 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>Este\ninterzis&#259; concedierea salaria&#355;ilor:</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_396394455\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1302\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_396394455\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)pe criterii de ras&#259;, cet&#259;&#355;enie, etnie,\nculoare, limb&#259;, religie, origine social&#259;, tr&#259;s&#259;turi\ngenetice, sex, orientare sexual&#259;, vârst&#259;, handicap, boal&#259;\ncronic&#259; necontagioas&#259;, infectare HIV, op&#355;iune politic&#259;,\nsitua&#355;ie sau responsabilitate familial&#259;, apartenen&#355;&#259; ori\nactivitate sindical&#259;, apartenen&#355;&#259; la o categorie\ndefavorizat&#259;;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>b)pentru\nexercitarea, în condi&#355;iile legii, a dreptului la grev&#259; &#351;i a\ndrepturilor sindicale.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_576289521\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1301\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_576289521\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)pentru exercitarea drepturilor prev&#259;zute la art. 17\nalin. (3), art. 18 alin. (1), art. 31, art. 39 alin. (1), art. 85 &#351;i art.\n194 alin. (2).</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}